    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A dull, discolored surface film caused by chemical deterioration, such as the film of silver sulfide that commonly forms on silver.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
